title: GAMESTAR CD: Horde - The Northern Wind - English
description:
Hello

This is my first torrent!


I cant find this very good old game on the internet, only russian...
My friend have 2 gamestar cd, with an english horde and a hungarian, but the dog ate the hungarian :D .
So i try to upload if somebody still want to play with this, i dont know its work or not, i will wait for comments.

The rar file includes all files from cd, demos and oter things, you just have to go in the install_eng folder and run setup.

Working for me on windows 7 without cd, without crack, with some very little texture bug.

Good game!
